<p class="courseblockdesc">
Introductory and cross-disciplinary examination of issues related to race, ethnicity, and cultural diversity in education. Course Information: Students need College approval to concurrently enroll in <a href="/search/?P=ED%20100" title="ED 100" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'ED 100');">ED 100</a> and <a href="/search/?P=ED%20205" title="ED 205" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'ED 205');">ED 205</a>.<i>  Individual and Society course, and  US Society course</i>.<br/>
